There used to be a monkey which lived on a tree. One day he wanted to go to the other side of 
the river since there were many fruit bearing trees.So he asked his friend to help him cross 
the river.The crocodile accepted to help the monkey.The crocodile went to his house.His wife told
him to betray the monkey.So the next day he took the monkey on his back.But his plan was to eat
the monkey.When they were halfway across the river the crocodile told the monkey that he would eat his
heart.